Step 1: Start ORBD (Naming Service)

Open a new terminal and run:

orbd -ORBInitialPort 1050


Step 2: Start the Server
Open another terminal, go to your project folder:
cd C:\Users\YASH\OneDrive\Desktop\DistributedPrograms\3-corba-java
Run the server:

java Server -ORBInitialHost localhost -ORBInitialPort 1050

Output should be:
Server ready...

Step 3: Start the Client
Open a third terminal, go to the project folder:
cd C:\Users\YASH\OneDrive\Desktop\DistributedPrograms\3-corba-java
Run the client:

java Client -ORBInitialHost localhost -ORBInitialPort 1050


Output should be:
Got reference to HelloService
Response from server: Hello, Student (from CORBA Server)